      "instruction": "<p><strong>Cook the jumbo king prawns</strong></p>\n<p>Heat a separate frying pan (preferably non-stick) with a knob of <strong>butter</strong> and drizzle of <strong>olive</strong> <strong>oil </strong>over a high heat.</p>\n<p>Pat the <strong>jumbo king prawns</strong> dry with kitchen roll.</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the<strong> jumbo king prawns</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 minutes, turning frequently, or until cooked through. </p>",
