      "instruction": "<p><strong>Serve <span class=\"text-highlight\">up!</span></strong></p>\n<p>Combine the <strong>chicory</strong>, <strong>grapes</strong> and<strong> balsamic dressing</strong> and give everything a good mix up.</p>\n<p>Serve the <strong>jumbo king prawns</strong> over the<strong> chorizo &amp; saffron risotto </strong>and spoon over any juices from the prawn pan.</p>\n<p>Sprinkle over the<strong> remaining parsley </strong>and garnish with a<strong> lemon wedge</strong>.</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
